직류를 인가한 경우 \text{L=0}이므로 \text{R} = \frac{\text{V}}{\text{I}} = \frac{\text{100}}{\text{20}} = \text{5[\Omega]}
교류를 인가한 경우 임피던스 \text{Z} = \frac{\text{V}}{\text{I}} = \frac{\text{100}}{\text{10}} = \text{10[\Omega]}
\text{Z} = \sqrt{\text{R}^2 + \text{X}_L^2} 이므로 \text{X}_L = \sqrt{\text{Z}^2 - \text{R}^2} = \sqrt{\text{10}^2 - \text{5}^2} = \sqrt{\text{75}} = \text{5}\sqrt{\text{3}}[\Omega]

